<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<meta name="author" content="Memorygraph Wedding Studio"/>
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow"/>
<meta name="description" content="A curated portfolio of cinematic Kerala wedding stories — temple weddings, heritage venues, destinations. Photographed and filmed by Memorygraph Wedding Studio."/>
<meta name="keywords" content="Kerala Wedding Stories, Temple Wedding Photography, Heritage Venue Wedding, Destination Wedding Kerala, Memorygraph Portfolio"/>
<title>Wedding Stories | Real Kerala Weddings | Memorygraph</title>
<meta property="og:title" content="Wedding Stories | Real Kerala Weddings | Memorygraph"/>
<meta property="og:description" content="A curated portfolio of cinematic Kerala wedding stories — temple weddings, heritage venues, destinations."/>
<meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
<meta property="og:url" content="https://memorygraphweddings.com/stories/"/>
<meta property="og:image" content="https://memorygraphweddings.com/assets/og-stories.jpg"/>
<meta property="og:locale" content="en_IN"/>
<meta property="og:site_name" content="Memorygraph Weddings"/>
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/>
<meta name="twitter:title" content="Wedding Stories | Real Kerala Weddings | Memorygraph"/>
<meta name="twitter:description" content="A curated portfolio of cinematic Kerala wedding stories — temple weddings, heritage venues, destinations."/>
<meta name="twitter:image" content="https://memorygraphweddings.com/assets/og-stories.jpg"/>
<link rel="canonical" href="https://memorygraphweddings.com/stories/"/>

<!-- Fonts -->
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,500&family=Jost:wght@200;300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

<!-- Shared Animation CSS -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/animations.css"/>

<style>
  *,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  :root{
    --ivory:#f4ede0;--ivory-2:#ece4d4;--ink:#1a1814;--ink-soft:#3a3530;
    --teal:#1d5959;--teal-2:#2a7575;--teal-deep:#0f3838;
    --gold:#b8965a;--gold-2:#d4a96a;--mist:#8b857a;
    --line:rgba(26,24,20,.12);--line-2:rgba(26,24,20,.06);
    --serif:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;--sans:'Jost',sans-serif;
  }
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{background:var(--ivory);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:300;overflow-x:hidden;cursor:none;}
  body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:1;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 400 400' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='.85' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");mix-blend-mode:multiply;opacity:.6;}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){body{cursor:auto;}.cursor{display:none;}}
  @media (pointer: coarse) { body { cursor: auto; } .cursor { display: none; } }

  .cursor{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;z-index:9999;pointer-events:none;}
  .cursor-dot{width:5px;height:5px;background:var(--teal);border-radius:50%;position:absolute;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);mix-blend-mode:difference;}
  .cursor-ring{width:28px;height:28px;border:1px solid rgba(29,89,89,.4);border-radius:50%;position:absolute;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:width .3s,height .3s,border-color .3s,background .3s;}
  .cursor-ring.hover{width:48px;height:48px;border-color:var(--teal);background:rgba(29,89,89,.06);}

  /* NAV */
  nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;z-index:100;padding:24px 56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;transition:padding .5s,background .5s,transform .4s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);}
  nav.scrolled{padding:14px 56px;background:rgba(244,237,224,.92);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-2);}
  .nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink);}
  .nav-wordmark{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.04em;color:var(--ink);line-height:1;}
  .nav-wordmark small{display:block;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.55rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.32em;color:var(--mist);margin-top:4px;}
  .nav-links{display:flex;gap:42px;list-style:none;}
  .nav-links a{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.7rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft);text-decoration:none;transition:color .3s;position:relative;}
  .nav-links a::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-4px;left:0;width:0;height:1px;background:var(--teal);transition:width .4s;}
  .nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{color:var(--teal);}
  .nav-links a:hover::after,.nav-links a.active::after{width:100%;}
  .nav-cta{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--teal);color:var(--ivory);padding:11px 26px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .35s;border:1px solid var(--teal);display:inline-block;}
  .nav-cta:hover{background:var(--teal-deep);border-color:var(--teal-deep);}

  /* PAGE HERO */
  .page-hero{padding:200px 56px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
  .page-hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;width:50%;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%,rgba(184,150,90,.15) 0%,transparent 60%);}
  .ph-label{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.35em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
  .ph-label::before{content:'';width:32px;height:1px;background:var(--teal);}
  .page-hero h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(4rem,8vw,9rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1;color:var(--ink);position:relative;}
  .page-hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--teal);}
  .ph-sub{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.92rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:32px;max-width:520px;line-height:1.9;}
  .ph-count{position:absolute;right:56px;bottom:80px;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:7rem;font-weight:300;color:rgba(29,89,89,.08);line-height:1;user-select:none;}
  .ph-count em{font-style:italic;}

  /* FILTER */
  .filter-bar{padding:48px 56px;display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;border-top:1px solid var(--line-2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-2);background:var(--ivory-2);}
  .filter-btn{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:9px 18px;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink-soft);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;}
  .filter-btn.active,.filter-btn:hover{border-color:var(--teal);color:var(--teal);background:var(--ivory);}

  /* FEATURED */
  .featured{padding:100px 56px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-2);}
  .feat-img{position:relative;}
  .feat-frame{width:100%;padding-bottom:120%;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#d8cfb8 0%,#a89a78 100%);position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
  .feat-frame::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 40% 35%,rgba(29,89,89,.12) 0%,transparent 65%);}
  .feat-frame::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='.9' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='.15'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");mix-blend-mode:multiply;}
  .ph-icon{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
  .ph-icon svg{opacity:.18;}
  .feat-badge{position:absolute;top:32px;left:-14px;background:var(--teal);color:var(--ivory);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.58rem;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:8px 20px;z-index:2;}
  .feat-corner{position:absolute;bottom:-14px;right:-14px;width:90px;height:90px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--gold);border-right:1px solid var(--gold);}
  .feat-play{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:88px;height:88px;border:1px solid var(--ivory);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--ivory);background:rgba(26,24,20,.35);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);transition:all .35s;cursor:pointer;}
  .feat-play:hover{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.08);background:rgba(26,24,20,.55);}
  .feat-play svg{width:20px;height:20px;margin-left:3px;}
  .feat-meta{}
  .feat-label{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:18px;}
  .feat-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2.4rem,4vw,4rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.1;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:12px;}
  .feat-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--teal);}
  .feat-loc{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mist);margin-bottom:32px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
  .feat-loc::before{content:'';width:20px;height:1px;background:var(--mist);}
  .feat-quote{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-style:italic;line-height:1.75;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:36px;border-left:2px solid var(--gold);padding-left:24px;}
  .feat-stats{display:flex;gap:48px;margin-bottom:44px;}
  .feat-stat strong{display:block;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:2rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--teal);}
  .feat-stat span{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mist);}
  .btn-story{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);text-decoration:none;border:1px solid var(--teal);padding:14px 32px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;transition:all .35s;}
  .btn-story:hover{background:var(--teal);color:var(--ivory);}

  /* GRID */
  .grid-section{padding:100px 56px 140px;}
  .grid-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--mist);margin-bottom:48px;font-style:italic;}
  .stories-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:3px;}
  .story-card{position:relative;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;}
  .s-img{width:100%;padding-bottom:130%;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
  .s-img-inner{position:absolute;inset:0;transition:transform .8s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1),filter .8s;filter:grayscale(60%);}
  .story-card:hover .s-img-inner{transform:scale(1.05);filter:grayscale(0%);}
  .sg1{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#d8cfb8 0%,#b8a98a 100%);}
  .sg2{background:linear-gradient(140deg,#cdc1a8 0%,#aa9a7a 100%);}
  .sg3{background:linear-gradient(150deg,#c9bda1 0%,#a09177 100%);}
  .sg4{background:linear-gradient(170deg,#d2c8b0 0%,#b3a48a 100%);}
  .sg5{background:linear-gradient(155deg,#cdc0a4 0%,#9e8f70 100%);}
  .sg6{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#d4c8ac 0%,#ad9e7e 100%);}
  .s-noise{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='.85' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='.15'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");mix-blend-mode:multiply;}
  .s-meta-block{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:24px 28px;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(244,237,224,.95) 0%,rgba(244,237,224,.85) 50%,rgba(244,237,224,0) 100%);}
  .s-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.25rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:4px;}
  .s-meta{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);}
  .s-tag{position:absolute;top:24px;left:24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.55rem;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ivory);background:rgba(26,24,20,.55);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);padding:6px 12px;}
  .s-tag.video{background:var(--teal);}
  .s-hover{position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(26,24,20,.4);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;opacity:0;transition:opacity .35s;}
  .story-card:hover .s-hover{opacity:1;}
  .s-hover-btn{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid rgba(244,237,224,.6);color:var(--ivory);padding:10px 22px;}

  /* PAGINATION */
  .pagination{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:8px;padding:60px 0 0;}
  .pg-btn{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.7rem;width:42px;height:42px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink-soft);cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;text-decoration:none;}
  .pg-btn.active,.pg-btn:hover{border-color:var(--teal);color:var(--teal);}

  /* CTA STRIP */
  .cta-strip{padding:120px 56px;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--teal-deep) 0%,var(--teal) 100%);color:var(--ivory);position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
  .cta-strip::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%,rgba(184,150,90,.1) 0%,transparent 60%);}
  .cs-label{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.35em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:24px;}
  .cs-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2.4rem,4vw,4rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:20px;position:relative;z-index:1;}
  .cs-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-2);}
  .cs-sub{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.9rem;font-weight:300;color:rgba(244,237,224,.7);margin-bottom:40px;position:relative;z-index:1;}
  .btn-gold{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--gold);color:var(--teal-deep);padding:16px 40px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .35s;display:inline-block;border:1px solid var(--gold);position:relative;z-index:1;}
  .btn-gold:hover{background:var(--gold-2);}

  /* FOOTER */
  footer{background:var(--ink);color:var(--ivory);padding:60px 56px 36px;}
  .footer-inner{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:40px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:24px;}
  .footer-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
  .footer-logo svg{width:30px;height:24px;color:var(--ivory);}
  .footer-brand-text{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:500;line-height:1;}
  .footer-brand-text small{display:block;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.55rem;letter-spacing:.32em;color:var(--mist);margin-top:5px;}
  .footer-links-row{display:flex;gap:32px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .footer-links-row a{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.68rem;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(244,237,224,.45);text-decoration:none;transition:color .3s;}
  .footer-links-row a:hover{color:var(--gold);}
  .footer-bottom{border-top:1px solid rgba(244,237,224,.08);padding-top:24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px;}
  .footer-copy{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.65rem;color:rgba(244,237,224,.3);}

  /* WHATSAPP */
  .whatsapp-float{position:fixed;bottom:32px;right:32px;z-index:200;width:58px;height:58px;border-radius:50%;background:#25d366;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(37,211,102,.35);text-decoration:none;animation:pulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;}
  .whatsapp-float svg{width:30px;height:30px;color:#fff;}
  @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(37,211,102,.35);}50%{box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(37,211,102,.6),0 0 0 14px rgba(37,211,102,.05);}}

  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(36px);transition:opacity .9s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1),transform .9s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1);}
  .reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
  .reveal-d1{transition-delay:.15s;}
  .reveal-d2{transition-delay:.3s;}

  @media (max-width:980px){
    body{cursor:auto;} .cursor{display:none;}
    nav{padding:16px 20px;} nav.scrolled{padding:12px 20px;}
    .nav-links{display:none;}
    .page-hero{padding:140px 20px 60px;}
    .ph-count{font-size:4rem;right:20px;bottom:30px;}
    .filter-bar{padding:32px 20px;}
    .featured{padding:60px 20px;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:48px;}
    .grid-section{padding:60px 20px 80px;}
    .stories-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
    .cta-strip{padding:80px 24px;}
    footer{padding:40px 24px 28px;}
  }
  @media (max-width:600px){
    .stories-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .feat-stats{gap:24px;}
  }
  .story-card-link { display: block; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- PRELOADER -->
<div class="preloader" id="preloader">
  <div class="preloader-logo">
    Memorygraph
    <small>Photographing Memories</small>
  </div>
  <div class="preloader-line"></div>
</div>

<!-- PAGE TRANSITION OVERLAY -->
<div class="page-transition-overlay"></div>

<!-- THEME TOGGLE -->
<button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" aria-label="Toggle light/dark mode">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><path d="M12 1v2M12 21v2M4.22 4.22l1.42 1.42M18.36 18.36l1.42 1.42M1 12h2M21 12h2M4.22 19.78l1.42-1.42M18.36 5.64l1.42-1.42"/>
  </svg>
</button>

<!-- CURSOR -->
<div class="cursor" id="cursor"><div class="cursor-dot" id="cursorDot"></div><div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div></div>

<!-- LIGHTBOX -->
<div class="lightbox" id="lightbox">
  <button class="lightbox-close" aria-label="Close lightbox"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg></button>
  <button class="lightbox-nav lightbox-prev" aria-label="Previous image"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg></button>
  <img class="lightbox-img" src="" alt="Gallery image"/>
  <button class="lightbox-nav lightbox-next" aria-label="Next image"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg></button>
  <div class="lightbox-caption"></div>
</div>

<nav id="nav">
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
    <img src="/assets/logo/logo-dark.png" alt="Memorygraph Wedding Studio" style="height:48px;width:auto;max-width:160px;display:block;"/>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/stories/" class="active">Stories</a></li>
    <li><a href="/about/">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="/investment/">Investment</a></li>
    <li><a href="/blog/">Journal</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="/contact/" class="nav-cta magnetic">Begin Your Story</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="ph-label gsap-reveal">Wedding Stories</div>
  <h1 class="gsap-reveal reveal-d1 stagger-words">Love, told in<br><em>frames.</em></h1>
  <p class="ph-sub gsap-reveal reveal-d2">Every wedding we photograph becomes a story we carry with us. These are some of the ones that have left a permanent mark — the ones we still think about.</p>
</div>

<!-- FILTERS -->
<div class="filter-bar gsap-reveal">
  <button class="filter-btn active">All Stories</button>
  <button class="filter-btn">Temple Weddings</button>
  <button class="filter-btn">Heritage Venues</button>
  <button class="filter-btn">Destination</button>
  <button class="filter-btn">Backwaters</button>
  <button class="filter-btn">Intimate</button>
  <button class="filter-btn">With Film</button>
</div>

<!-- FEATURED -->
{% set featured = collections.stories[0] %}
<div class="featured">
  <div class="feat-img gsap-reveal">
    <div class="feat-badge">Featured &middot; Watch the Film</div>
    <div class="feat-frame" style="background-image:url('{{ featured.data.hero }}'); background-size:cover; background-position:center;">
      <div class="ph-icon">
        <svg width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none">
          <circle cx="50" cy="38" r="22" stroke="#1a1814" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <path d="M12 88c0-21 17-38 38-38s38 17 38 38" stroke="#1a1814" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-play" data-lightbox="{{ featured.data.hero }}" data-caption="{{ featured.data.title }}">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-corner"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="feat-meta gsap-reveal reveal-d1">
    <div class="feat-label">Most Recent &middot; 2024</div>
    <h2 class="feat-title">{{ featured.data.title }}</h2>
    <div class="feat-loc">{{ featured.data.location }}</div>
    <blockquote class="feat-quote">"A morning ceremony bathed in golden lamp-light, the scent of jasmine, and a couple who barely needed direction — they were too busy being in love."</blockquote>
    <div class="feat-stats">
      <div class="feat-stat"><strong>840</strong><span>Images</span></div>
